  }), mdx("p", null, "Serge leans back, a mischievous grin playing on his face, and says, \"You know, Max, there was a time when I encountered a metric so absurd, I had an existential crisis. It\u2019s all BS. Why even bother? I questioned the point of it all, ya know?\" His words pique my curiosity, and I lean in. His eye twinkles, Serge begins his story, transporting me to a world where data anomalies run rampant and the quest for truth takes an unexpected turn."), mdx("p", null, "Serge begins his story. This is Part II of, ", mdx("a", {
