ment effectively seeks to take away a person\u2019s agency. It makes them believe that they may be robbing God or will receive lesser blessings for paying on their net income. That\u2019s just not true. However you decide to pay your tithing, do it prayerfully and honestly. That\u2019s all God asks for."));
