    parentName: "p"
  }, "That recommendation is where I will start and finish this discussion."), " In the middle, we\u2019ll dive deep into the topic and discuss some questions you\u2019ve probably had and probably a few you\u2019ve never thought about."), mdx("h2", null, "The basics of tithing"), mdx("p", null, "A tithe is 10% of your income that you pay to the church. It pays for things like:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Chapels"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
